overview: Watch the mind-blasting comedy duo Sumukhi Suresh and Naveen Richard slip in and out of 14 outrageous characters, in 7 absurd sketches, all in 1 dangerously funny hour of live sketch comedy. One second Naveen is playing tennis and the in next, Sumukhi is playing a mosquito. Heart patients and close-minded individuals are not allowed on this ride.
title: Go Straight Take Left
